<p><strong>입출력 예시</strong></p>
<blockquote>
  <p>Input-1 <br />
<strong>A = [1, 4, 2]</strong> <br />
<strong>B = [5, 4, 4]</strong> <br />
Output-1 <br />
<strong>29</strong></p>
</blockquote>

<blockquote>
  <p>Input-2 <br />
<strong>A = [1, 2]</strong> <br />
<strong>B = [3, 4]</strong> <br />
Output-2 <br />
<strong>10</strong></p>
</blockquote>

<p><br /></p>

